        "subject": "LU-5170 lfs: Standardize llapi messages from lfs_setdirstripe",
        "message": "LU-5170 lfs: Standardize llapi messages from lfs_setdirstripe\n\nError messages in the llapi functions called by lfs_setdirstripe()\nare updated to a standard format.  Messages are prefixed with\nthe name of the utility and the command that caused the error.\nUser-provided values are delimited with single quotes.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nSigned-off-by: Steve Guminski <stephenx.guminski@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I3e44e3d7303b81a8411a069bd9d57a216815b273\n"
      },
